replies.body:
I am sad to hear you might miss the Graves skin. If there is ever a victorious bard or fiddle skin and I miss it I might just cry.
{{sticker:cass-cry}} 

Concerning your language related punishment, I suppose it might very well be a misunderstanding on the part of your teammates. Where I live it is uncommon to be sworn at, so when someone does curse at you it is usually seen as a verbal attack. Usually in game there is not very much time to type so it can be especially difficult to decipher a person's tone from the limited text. This leads to many wife's jokes and missed sarchasm, but also some people seeing insults where none were intended.
{{sticker:zombie-brand-facepalm}} 

I hope your account gets back in good graces soon, and thanks for reminding me to be careful of how I say things.
{{sticker:vlad-salute}}
